high_descs: Turn right and go forward then turn right and face the coffee table.
Pick up the credit card from the coffee table.
Turn to the left and walk over to the blue armchair.
Place the credit card on the armchair.
Turn to the left and then left again to face the TV stand.
Pick up the credit card from the TV stand.
Turn to the left and walk over to the blue armchair.
Place the credit card on the armchair.
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards onto a blue armchair.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the side of the coffee table in front of the TV stand.
Pick the first card up to the right of the box.
Turn to the right and go to the front of the chair in the corner.
Place the card down on top of the chair cushion.
Turn around and go to the front of the TV stand.
Pick up the cart in front of the TV.
Turn to the left and go back to the chair in the corner.
Place the card down next to other one on top of the chair cushion.
anns.task_desc: Place two cards in the chair in the corner of the room.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room and walk around to face the opposite side of the living room table.
Pick up the card on the table.
Turn right and step forward to face the chair.
Place the card in the chair.
Turn around and step forward and turn right to face the living room table.
Pick up the card on the table.
Turn right and step forward to face the chair.
Place the card in the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move two cards from the living room table to the chair on the right side of the room.
